description_for_human: Plugin for fetching financial data from Alpha Vantage.
description_for_model: Plugin for fetching financial data from Alpha Vantage. The plugin provides four main functions: OVERVIEW, INCOME_STATEMENT, BALANCE_SHEET, and CASH_FLOW. Each function requires the symbol of the equity of interest. The model should use the plugin when the user requests financial data related to these functions and provides a valid equity symbol.
